OL,3,CHearing-impaired man settles case with
OL,4,CDAERA for #50k
OL,6,FA man whose hearing is impaired has
OL,7,Fsettled a disability discrimination
OL,8,Fcase against the Department of
OL,9,FAgriculture, Environment and Rural
OL,10,FAffairs for #50,000.
OL,12,FChristopher Morrow worked at
OL,13,FCrawfordsburn Park in Co Down, and in
OL,14,FFebruary 2021 he was interviewed for a
OL,15,Fpermanent job as a ranger at the park.
OL,17,FHe asked for reasonable adjustments to
OL,18,Fbe put in place, but found the
OL,19,Finterview environment very difficult
OL,20,Fand did not get one of the 15 jobs on
OL,21,Foffer.
