OL,3,CHearing-impaired man settles case with
OL,4,CDAERA for #50k
OL,6,FThere was no admission of liability.
OL,8,FMr Morrow said: "I tried on several
OL,9,Foccasions to make DAERA aware of my
OL,10,Fdisability and requested some simple
OL,11,Fadjustments at interview that would
OL,12,Fhave really helped me in the
OL,13,Frecruitment process.
OL,15,F"I was very disappointed indeed that I
OL,16,Fmissed out on the opportunity for a
OL,17,Fpermanent position in a job I really
OL,18,Fenjoyed.
