OL,6,F"I had a legal right to reasonable
OL,7,Fadjustments which would allow me to
OL,8,Fcompete on a level playing field, and
OL,9,FI think what I asked for was simple
OL,10,Fand straightforward."
OL,12,FThe case was supported by the Equality
OL,13,FCommission.
