OL,4,CDAERA for #50k
OL,6,F"The Disability Discrimination Act
OL,7,Frequires employers to introduce
OL,8,Freasonable adjustments to recruitment
OL,9,Fand selection procedures for
OL,10,Fapplicants with disabilities, to
OL,11,Fensure that disabled people are not
OL,12,Fdisadvantaged," said Mary Kitson,
OL,13,Fsenior legal officer at the Equality
OL,14,FCommission.
OL,16,F"The purpose of the duty is to enable
OL,17,Fjob applicants who have disabilities
OL,18,Fto enjoy the same opportunities as all
OL,19,Fother candidates to obtain and remain
OL,20,Fin work.
