OL,6,F"What is reasonable may be different
OL,7,Fin every case ` the law says employers
OL,8,Fmust take such steps as are reasonable
OL,9,Fto remove any physical or procedural
OL,10,Fbarriers which the disabled person may
OL,11,Fface when seeking work."
OL,13,FAs part of the settlement, DAERA, in
OL,14,Fconjunction with the Department of
OL,15,FFinance, has undertaken to liaise with
OL,16,Fthe Equality Commission to review its
OL,17,Fpolicies, practices and procedures and
OL,18,Ftheir application to ensure that they
OL,19,Fare effective and conform with
OL,20,Fdisability legislation.
